strings.Value: "I demand you to stop intimidating my subjects immediately!"
"I won't get in your way. Continue your investigation."
"Where is {d|Darven}Darven{/d} now? Speak up, or else!"
"I don't know who you're talking about! Let me go! What do you think you're doing?!"
"The man who spent last night at your place is a fugitive and a criminal!"
"I didn't know he was a criminal! He asked to spend a night on my floor, then he left in the morning! I don't know anything else!"
"I let the traveler inside for the night, that's all. He paid me, and left in the morning! I didn't talk with him, and I didn't know who he was! Please, help me!"
"Maybe, he's telling the truth. Or maybe not. Soon we'll find out."
